#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.47:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Sagāthakapuññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "5. Overflowing Merit, With Verses "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Nandiyasutta "
msgstr "47. With Nandiya "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.47:1.1"
msgid "Kapilavatthunidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Kapilavatthu. "

msgctxt "sn55.47:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho nandiyaṃ sakkaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, the Buddha said to Nandiya the Sakyan: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.47:1.3"
msgid "“catūhi kho, nandiya, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo. "
msgstr "“Nandiya, a noble disciple who has four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.47:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.47:2.2"
msgid "Idha, nandiya, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.47:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.47:2.4"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.47:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.47:2.6"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.47:2.7"
msgid "Imehi kho, nandiya, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo”ti. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.47:2.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
